Intel Encoding

                Prefixes   -    Opcode   -      ModR/M      -   SIB     -       Displacement    -       Immediate 
size (bytes)    1 ea. opt.      1/2/3           1 opt.          1 opt.          1/2/4 opt.              1/2/4 opt. *

ModR/M (1 byte, 3 fields)
00      000             000
Mod     Reg/Opcode      R/M

SIB (1 byte, 3 fields)
00      000             000
Scale   Index           Base

* Some rare instructions can take an 8 byte immediate or displacement 
